    • removeBorder

      public void removeBorder(byte borderDeletion)
      Removes sides of borders in total. Required by insertion of column/rows as inserted cell borders depend on preceding invalid input: '&' following cell borders. Only identical sides will be kept.

      borderDeletion - removes the borders as given in byte
